    { place:'Near Village Vanguard Shimokitazawa', lat:35.6612, lng:139.6685, episode:'Episode 2', time:'Noon', desc:'An area well known for recreating the anime city scenery. Visitors can experience the unique subculture atmosphere that defines Bocchi the Rock.', access:'About 2 minutes on foot from Shimokitazawa Station' },
